lmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|title=Gravity Noir|last=AllMusic|first=Discography|date=2016-11-30|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110093113/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|archive-date=2019-11-10|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''Liberation''  2017  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191924097662)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4kVDpT7mCM&list=OLAK5uy_mKmWl_dmyfTowUcW-qdtu4C6xsT8Y-rTY|title=Gravity Noir Liberation|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2017-11-09|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|title=Gravity Noir|last=AllMusic|first=Discography|date=2016-11-30|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110093113/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|archive-date=2019-11-10|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''The Singles''  2017  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191924217718)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7R9uaJD7oI&list=OLAK5uy_lVn0q25uaazGs0Xy-OPoLl2GXf10-E28Y|title=Gravity Noir The Singles|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2017-08-19|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref>\n* ''The Remixes''  2017  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191924450573)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jAhuxvdAqjY&list=OLAK5uy_kjh3K071598lu_2g-2-n_inyYhbjALtEk|title=Gravity Noir The Remixes|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2017-04-08|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref>\n* ''Future Days''  2020  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 192914889168)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/be/album/future-days/1489030385?l=en|title=Future Days by Gravity Noir|last=Music|first=Apple|date=2020-03-18|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref>\n\n; EPs\n\n* ''Welcome to My Gravity''  2016  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191061056942)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ascap.com/repertory#ace/search/title/welcome%20to